Sentence 0:
The TrpD2 proteins show high structural homology to anthranilate phosphoribosyltransferase (TrpD) and nucleoside phosphorylase class II enzymes but bind with high affinity (KD = 10-100 nM) to nucleic acids without detectable sequence specificity.
sentence_raw: The TrpD2 proteins show high structural homology to anthranilate phosphoribosyltransferase (TrpD) and nucleoside phosphorylase class II enzymes but bind with high affinity (KD = 10-100 nM) to nucleic acids without detectable sequence specificity.
